{"title":"遥寄祖国亲人","authors":["张文英"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":2,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥寄祖国亲人遥寄祖国亲人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张文英"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，是除夕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我扑通扑通的心儿，漂洋过海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像又回到了故里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春联耀眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红灯闪烁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“福”字“倒”门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰年的瑞雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫天飞舞，迷迷离离。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"午夜的钟声敲响，这是喜庆的乐章，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它——奏响了民富国强的主旋律。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁没有年迈的父母？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁没有兄弟姐妹，妻子儿女？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又有谁的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是同祖国和亲人紧紧相依？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，是除夕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，远涉重洋的我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并不觉得孤寂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为我肩负的是祖国的使命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是生活在一个温暖的集体里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻的外交官"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许是第一次在国外过除夕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但如果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你问两鬓如霜的大使"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他肯定会笑着告诉你："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“有多少次在国外过除夕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我已记忆不起！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个职业外交官，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼观四海风云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耳听五洲雷霆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸怀的——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是民族的希望和志气！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他日夜出没在没有硝烟的战场上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"始终为祖国战斗不息！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，是除夕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然，在我感情的网络上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布满拂之不去的惦记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但使馆就是我的家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把酒杯高高举起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄意那太平洋的涛声浪语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就如同"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和祖国和亲人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团聚在一起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者系中国驻厄瓜多尔使馆一等秘书）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}